OL,3,CPetition calls to cancel costly by-
OL,4,Celection for disgraced ex-politician
OL,6,FA Guernsey petition wants a proposed
OL,7,Fby-election to replace convicted
OL,8,Fpaedophile Jonathan Le Tocq scrapped.
OL,10,FLe Tocq submitted his resignation
OL,11,Fafter pleading guilty to 15 sexual
OL,12,Foffences, including possessing more
OL,13,Fthan 2,400 indecent images of children.
OL,15,FPoliticians have now voted to formally
OL,16,Faccept Le Tocq's resignation, which
OL,17,Fwill trigger the island's first-ever
OL,18,Fby-election under the new island-wide
OL,19,Fvoting system first used in 2020.
