OL,3,CPetition calls to cancel costly by-
OL,4,Celection for disgraced ex-politician
OL,6,FHowever, a public petition to stop the
OL,7,Fby-election, set up by local man
OL,8,FRichard Van Vliet, has now garnered
OL,9,Fmore than 300 signatures.
OL,11,FMr Van Vliet told ITV News there are
OL,12,Fconcerns over how much the by-election
OL,13,Fwill cost the island.
OL,15,FIt is estimated that it could cost the
OL,16,FStates of Guernsey up to #200,000.
