OL,3,CPetition calls to cancel costly by-
OL,4,Celection for disgraced ex-politician
OL,6,F"I appreciate everybody has a
OL,7,FDemocratic right to have their say,"
OL,8,FMr Van Fliet explained. "And we are
OL,9,Fentitled to increase the number of
OL,10,FStates members, but in these
OL,11,Fcircumstances, under these conditions,
OL,12,FI think spending this kind of money is
OL,13,Freally unnecessary."
OL,15,FMr Van Vliet has also questioned
OL,16,Fwhether the States need to replace Le
OL,17,FTocq.
