OL,3,CPetition calls to cancel costly by-
OL,4,Celection for disgraced ex-politician
OL,6,F"There's no need to have one more
OL,7,Fperson at this stage - maybe if we had
OL,8,Fto replace three or four seats, then I
OL,9,Fthink it would be a different matter,"
OL,10,Fhe added.
OL,12,F"This is a longer-term view about the
OL,13,Ffinances of the island and the use of
OL,14,Fthe resources we have."
OL,16,FMr Van Vliet also believes Guernsey
OL,17,Flocals may be suffering from election
OL,18,Ffatigue and believes "there won't be
OL,19,Fmuch interest" in a by-election.
