OL,6,FGuernsey's Chief Minister, Deputy
OL,7,FLindsay de Sausmarez, told ITV News
OL,8,Fthat one of the first States Assembly
OL,9,Fdebates this political term determined
OL,10,Fa by-election would be "significantly
OL,11,Fless costly than the original
OL,12,Festimates suggested".
